Package net.sf.jclal.core

The package contains the core of the framework.

See: Description

    Interface Description
    IAlgorithm
    Algorithm interface.
    IAlgorithmListener
    Algorithm listener.
    IBatchMode
    Interface for batch mode active learning.
    IClassifier
    Interface for the classifiers to be used in the framework.
    IConfigure
    Class for the configuration of the experiments by XML format.
    IDataset
    Interface that represents a dataset.
    IEvaluation
    It represents a interface for all evaluation metrics.
    IEvaluationMethod
    Evaluation method used to analyze the performance of an experiment.
